  "problemTitle": "월향 수목원",
  "bojProblemId": "34662",
  "infoHtml": "<thead><tr><th style=\"width:16%;\">시간 제한</th><th style=\"width:16%;\">메모리 제한</th><th style=\"width:17%;\">제출</th><th style=\"width:17%;\">정답</th><th style=\"width:17%;\">맞힌 사람</th><th style=\"width:17%;\">정답 비율</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>3.5 초 </td><td>1024 MB</td><td>149</td><td>38</td><td>12</td><td>27.273%</td></tr></tbody>",
  "bodyHtml": "\n\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n\t\t\t\t<section id=\"description\"  class=\"problem-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"headline\">\n\t\t\t\t<h2>문제</h2>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"problem_description\" class=\"problem-text\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>월향 수목원은 최근 $N$개의 식물을 심었다. 초기에 식물들은 아직 영양분을 받지 못한 상태다.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>$i$번 식물은 $A_i$ 만큼의 영양분을 받으면 완전히 성장하며, 완전히 성장한 다음 날부터 구간 $[\\max(1,i-R_i),\\min(N,i+R_i)]$에 속한 식물들에 영양분을 매일 $V_i$ 만큼 공급하기 시작한다.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>월향 수목원의 관리자인 아이보리가 매일 모든 식물에 $1$만큼의 영양분을 준다고 할 때, 모든 식물이 완전히 성장하기 위해서는 적어도 며칠이 걸리는지 구해보자.</p>\r\n\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<section id=\"input\"  class=\"problem-section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"headline\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2>입력</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"problem_input\" class=\"problem-text\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>첫째 줄에 정수 $N$이 주어진다. $(1\\leq N \\leq 200\\,000)$</p>\r\n\r\n<p>둘째 줄부터 $N$개의 줄에 걸쳐 정수 $A_i, R_i, V_i$ 가 공백으로 구분되어 주어진다. $(1 \\leq A_i, V_i \\leq 200\\,000; 1\\leq R_i \\leq N)$</p>\r\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<section id=\"output\"  class=\"problem-section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"headline\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2>출력</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"problem_output\" class=\"problem-text\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>모든 식물이 완전히 성장하는 데 필요한 최소 일수를 출력한다.</p>\r\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n\t\t\t<section id=\"limit\" style=\"display:none;\" class=\"problem-section\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"headline\">\n\t\t\t<h2>제한</h2>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div id=\"problem_limit\" class=\"problem-text\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section id=\"sampleinput1\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"headline\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>예제 입력 1\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<pre class=\"sampledata\" id=\"sample-input-1\">4\n1 3 1\n2 1 1\n3 1 1\n5 1 1\n</pre>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section id=\"sampleoutput1\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"headline\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>예제 출력 1\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<pre class=\"sampledata\" id=\"sample-output-1\">3\n</pre>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section id=\"sampleinput2\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"headline\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>예제 입력 2\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<pre class=\"sampledata\" id=\"sample-input-2\">10\n17 1 4\n6 4 5\n19 3 4\n3 4 2\n4 4 5\n9 4 1\n8 2 3\n3 3 3\n3 4 1\n2 1 2\n</pre>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section id=\"sampleoutput2\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"headline\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>예제 출력 2\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<pre class=\"sampledata\" id=\"sample-output-2\">5\n</pre>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n\t\t\t\t<section id=\"hint\" style=\"display: none;\" class=\"problem-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"headline\">\n\t\t\t\t<h2>노트</h2>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"problem_hint\" class=\"problem-text\">\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12\"><section id=\"source\"><div class=\"headline\"><h2>출처</h2></div><p>Contest&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;BOJ User Contest&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;월간 향유회&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;월간 향유회 2025. 10.&nbsp;C번</p><ul><li>문제를 만든 사람:&nbsp;kaorin</li><li>문제를 검수한 사람:&nbsp;jthis, pyb1031, snrnsidy, tony